Package com.ocelot.api.utils

General utilities that may come in handy.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Buffers
    Allows the ability to easily store data in the buffers for the default data types.
    GuiUtils
    This class contains some utility methods that would be most useful when rendering a GUI.
    GuiUtils.GuiType
    Specifies the type of gui to draw.
    InventoryUtils
    Has some useful methods for getting, removing, and dealing with item stacks.
    OnlineRequest
    Requests information from the Internet asynchronously.
    TextureUtils
    Contains some methods to bind and manipulate textures easier.
    WorldUtils
    Contains some methods that help when manipulating the world.
